  "Description": {
    "English": "A deployable static platform, allowing the user to comfortably survey the seas in any weather. As well as providing a steady and easily accessible fishing spot, the Exo-Skiff also features abundant <span class=\"name name-technology\">Cold Storage</span>, granting additional space to store your catch. <br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Summon</span> the Exo-Skiff to any suitable body of water using the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "可部署的静态平台，允许使用者在所有气候条件下惬意观赏海洋风光。除此以外还能够提供稳定而且方便的钓鱼点，强化快艇内置有容量充足的<span class=\"name name-technology\">冷藏箱</span>，能够为你提供存放渔获的额外空间。<br><br>使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）在符合条件的水体上<span class=\"name name-stellar\">召唤</span>强化快艇。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "可部署的固定平台，方便使用者無懼天候舒適地探勘海洋。強化艇不僅提供穩定、方便的釣魚地點，更備有容量龐大的<span class=\"name name-technology\">冷藏庫</span>，利用額外的空間儲藏漁獲。<br><br>使用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 在任何適合的水域中<span class=\"name name-stellar\">召喚</span>強化艇。"
  },
